{"about_the_game":"A strategy/action RPG.  Smash through enemy ranks with one of six HERO-ish champions.  Assemble your troops and equip powerful spells to wage war across three different campaigns. Then climb the PvP ranks in fast-paced 1v1 or 2v2 competitive battles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Hero\u2026 or Villain?</h2>Play as one of six HERO-ish champions from the Imperial, Cursed, or Feral factions, all with unique abilities and play-styles.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876350/extras/hero_lineup_SM.png?t=1680711029\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Battle alongside your minions</h2>Summon hordes of skeletons, ferocious bearzerkers, or healing clerics.  Pick from dozens of minion types to fight by your side, many with special abilities.  Picking minions that work well together is key to victory.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876350/extras/Flynn_Attack_Fort.gif?t=1680711029\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore three unique campaigns</h2>Take part in an epic story that unfolds across three campaigns.  Explore the map, collect new minions, level up, and upgrade your deck.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876350/extras/map.gif?t=1680711029\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Might, magic &amp; mischief</h2>A well-timed spell can turn the tide of battle.  Use your mana wisely to unleash devastating attacks, empowering auras, or devious traps.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876350/extras/takedown.gif?t=1680711029\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Dive into multiplayer</h2>Test your skill in fast-paced 1v1 or 2v2 cross-platform brawls.  Build custom decks and play against friends, bots, or climb the ranked ladder.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876350/extras/Lobby_sm.gif?t=1680711029\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Hero's Journey","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1876350/26094b978413be4b7461a6c132f4714d554bf49c.jpg"},{"name":"Burning Bridges","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1876350/c720f6695c1c3fe6183190f282ca72d4fb4c95b7.jpg"},{"name":"Final Exams","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1876350/15b04d1101cf1fc460d1130704948ad8df3b06a7.jpg"},{"name":"Tribes United","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1876350/2489f1cbbbca2b1a21d3f08601ecc8e1813a2807.jpg"},{"name":"Gold Digging","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1876350/b7d2ab3e71132c47e779270661dce9ebabbc14f0.jpg"},{"name":"Unstoppable meets Unmovable","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1876350/01376d79aece5cc63d4f11d2255d0cecd42a5335.jpg"},{"name":"Active Bears in Area","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1876350/89a8117352d6bcae844a32c4b7a5f9cfb0027b7c.jpg"},{"name":"Rebel Scum","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1876350/d45ac7d04985fc9df62d5a7aa21e970718694a49.jpg"},{"name":"Curse Crushing","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1876350/d490baab4d652b25464511de347f26cc9b0eee32.jpg"},{"name":"Concert Crashers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1876350/b7068ec85cc9c2f28eb62b9d29ad07b15f5a991f.jpg"}],"total":28},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876350/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1680711029","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876350/page.bg.jpg?t=1680711029","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876350/capsule_231x8